achette livre in  the following legend appeared on its newly published books until warner books was renamed grand central publishing warner books and the w logo are trademarks of time warner inc or an affiliated company used under license by hachette book group usa which is not affiliated with time warner inc however no such legal fineprint notice has ever appeared on any warner music product since it was sold by time warner  warner music group statement regarding emi proposal wmg may   retrieved march     profile british music giant emi bbc news january   retrieved march     analysis wmgs moves could make room for ma  leeds jeff december   amazon to sell warner music minus copy protection the new york times retrieved december     digital sales surpass cds at atlantic  michael fitzgerald july   take us to the river how warner music and its musicians are combating declining album sales fast company   what ever happened to pearlyrics december   retrieved august     spotify ab october   spotify announces licensing deals and upcoming launch prnewswirecouk   ian youngs february   warner retreats from free music streaming bbc news   smith ethan september   mtv overtakes vevo as top online music destination wall street journal speakeasy blog   yinka adegoke may   blavatniks access wins warner music for  billion reuters retrieved may     wilkerson david b warner music to be sold in  billion cash deal  smith ethan may   deal values warner music at  billion wall street journal retrieved may     warner music group being sold for  billion to access industries amid industry decline washington post ap may   retrieved may   dead link  christman ed august   warner music ceo edgar bronfman jr and chairman stephen cooper switch jobs billboard retrieved january     updated edgar bronfman jr to step down as warner music group chairman no successor named billboard december   retrieved january     warner music group to acquire the parlophone label group wmg retrieved february     ingham 