outube and warner music group were in a multiyear deal with the two in january  there were new reports of the sites accounts containing covered songs being completely closed due to intervention by wmg and it appears that an end solution has not been found as of february   music streaming servicesedit in february  ceo edgar bronfman jr said that wmg will stop licensing its songs to free music streaming services he said that the focus will be on services that require payment creating an increase in boycotts of the label the label also drew criticism for refusing to put its music on googles music site google music but relented a year after the public release of google music with an announcement on october   that it had added its music portfolio to googles offerings see alsoedit companies portal list of record labels list of warner music group artists referencesedit  warner music group corp company profile – yahoo finance bizyahoocom retrieved february     a b christman ed july   access industries completes acquisition of warner music group billboard retrieved january     warner music canada ltd – the canadian encyclopedia  david seay august   wea at  billboard p    goodman  p   a b stay tuned by stan cornyn maitland moves on rhinocom   goodman  pp –  goodman  p   kinney record group international   a b seay  p   time warner landmarks ketupanet   kinney set up distrib corp to handle labels in  key cities billboard july   p    brian blevins march   kinneycbs enters joint distrib and pressing deal in england billboard p    kinney group gets rolling stones disks billboard april   p    connie bruck november   master of the game retrieved august     goodman  pp –  goodman  pp –   top  cash box archives   super seventies almanac   timeline warner music group  retrieved january     roger cohen december   the creator of time warner steven j ross is dead at  new york times retrieved february     a b c d e f g chuck philips may   warner music chief expected to quit today los ange